I believe Patrick just posted something today:

SDS 2023-24 | Product Releases & Updates General Forum
Here is how the motor shaft spacers included in the Kraken pinion kits should be used. Steering motor: 1/8" spacer above pinion 3/8" spacer above pinion Drive motor: 1/8" spacer below pinion 3/8" spacer above pinion This screenshot shows the Kraken spacers installed. [image]

Hope that helps! If you have more questions, definitely just ask in the SDS thread I linked! Patrick can answer anything directly.
